title: Get Out Of Stress. App
text: Get Out Of Stress. App Stress app very informative and has information about decreasing the stress many of ways causes symptoms relieve long term stress with certain solutions for it. Also has yoga section I haven't used. Know it would be helpful. Also gives ways to make goals and meet the objectives if you followed the whole thing.

title: Perspective and Tools for stress management
text: Perspective and Tools for stress management Great perspective on what stress is, how it impacts us and how we can improve our experience with it in our lives. It depersonalized the experience of stress and broke down the negative impact stress has. Good easy suggestions for counteracting stress.
